## Proposed Changes

### Fase 1: Cache Infrastructure — Service Class & Model Observers

Membuat fondasi cache invalidation otomatis. Setiap kali data diubah (create/update/delete), cache terkait akan di-flush secara otomatis oleh Observer.

#### [NEW] [CacheService.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/Diana_fashion/diana_fashion_app/app/Services/CacheService.php)
Centralized cache helper class yang mendefinisikan semua cache key dan TTL:
```php
class CacheService
{
    // === Cache Key Prefixes ===
    const STOREFRONT_PRODUCTS        = 'storefront:products';
    const STOREFRONT_RECOMMENDATIONS = 'arima_storefront_recommendations';
    const DASHBOARD_METRICS          = 'admin:dashboard:metrics';
    const ADMIN_PRODUCTS_LIST        = 'admin:products:list';
    const ADMIN_ORDERS_HISTORY       = 'admin:orders:history';
    const ADMIN_CUSTOMERS_LIST       = 'admin:customers:list';
    const ADMIN_STAFF_LIST           = 'admin:staff:list';
    const ARIMA_CONFIG               = 'admin:arima:config';
    const ARIMA_LOGS                 = 'admin:arima:logs';
    const POS_PRODUCTS_SEARCH        = 'pos:products:search';
    const POS_ONLINE_QUEUE           = 'pos:online:queue';

    // === TTL Registry (detik) ===
    const TTL_STOREFRONT      = 600;    // 10 menit — katalog produk publik
    const TTL_DASHBOARD       = 300;    // 5 menit — metrik agregasi
    const TTL_ADMIN_LIST      = 300;    // 5 menit — daftar admin (produk, order, dll)
    const TTL_ARIMA_CONFIG    = 3600;   // 1 jam — konfigurasi ARIMA jarang berubah
    const TTL_ARIMA_LOGS      = 120;    // 2 menit — log prediksi terbaru
    const TTL_POS_QUEUE       = 60;     // 1 menit — antrean pesanan real-time
    const TTL_RECOMMENDATIONS = 43200;  // 12 jam — rekomendasi AI storefront

    // Helper: generate unique cache key dari prefix + query params
    public static function key(string $prefix, array $params = []): string;

    // Helper: flush semua cache entry yang dimulai dengan prefix tertentu
    // Menggunakan query LIKE pada tabel `cache` karena driver database
    public static function flushByPrefix(string $prefix): void;

    // Helper: flush semua cache terkait produk
    public static function flushProductCaches(): void;

    // Helper: flush semua cache terkait order/transaksi
    public static function flushOrderCaches(): void;

    // Helper: flush semua cache terkait user
    public static function flushUserCaches(): void;

    // Helper: flush SELURUH cache aplikasi
    public static function flushAll(): void;

    // Helper: dapatkan daftar kategori cache + jumlah key aktif (untuk UI Settings)
    public static function getStats(): array;
}
```

> [!NOTE]
> Karena menggunakan driver `database`, method `flushByPrefix()` akan melakukan query `DELETE FROM cache WHERE key LIKE 'prefix%'` langsung ke tabel cache di Supabase. Ini efisien karena prefix sudah terstruktur.

#### [NEW] [ProductObserver.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/Diana_fashion/diana_fashion_app/app/Observers/ProductObserver.php)
Observer pada model `Product` — menangkap event `created`, `updated`, `deleted`:
- Memanggil `CacheService::flushProductCaches()` → menghapus cache:
  - `storefront:products:*` (katalog publik)
  - `admin:products:list:*` (daftar produk admin)
  - `pos:products:search:*` (pencarian produk POS)
  - `arima_storefront_recommendations` (rekomendasi AI)

#### [NEW] [OrderObserver.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/Diana_fashion/diana_fashion_app/app/Observers/OrderObserver.php)
Observer pada model `Order` — menangkap event `created`, `updated`:
- Memanggil `CacheService::flushOrderCaches()` → menghapus cache:
  - `admin:dashboard:metrics:*` (metrik pendapatan)
  - `admin:orders:history:*` (riwayat transaksi)
  - `pos:online:queue` (antrean pesanan web)
  - `admin:arima:logs` (log prediksi — data baru dapat mempengaruhi analisis)

#### [NEW] [UserObserver.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/Diana_fashion/diana_fashion_app/app/Observers/UserObserver.php)
Observer pada model `User` — menangkap event `created`, `updated`, `deleted`:
- Memanggil `CacheService::flushUserCaches()` → menghapus cache:
  - `admin:customers:list:*`
  - `admin:staff:list:*`

#### [MODIFY] [AppServiceProvider.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/Diana_fashion/diana_fashion_app/app/Providers/AppServiceProvider.php)
Mendaftarkan semua Observer pada method `boot()`:
```php
use App\Models\{Product, Order, User};
use App\Observers\{ProductObserver, OrderObserver, UserObserver};

public function boot(): void
{
    Product::observe(ProductObserver::class);
    Order::observe(OrderObserver::class);
    User::observe(UserObserver::class);
}
```

