### Fase 2: Caching Layer — Storefront Publik (Prioritas Tertinggi)

Storefront adalah entry point utama bagi pelanggan. Data produk relatif stabil sehingga caching 10 menit sangat efektif.

#### [MODIFY] [StorefrontController.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/Diana_fashion/diana_fashion_app/app/Http/Controllers/StorefrontController.php)

**`getProducts()`** — Cache TTL: 10 menit
- Key di-hash berdasarkan kombinasi: `category`, `keyword`, `sort`, `page`
- Saat `ProductObserver` terpicu, seluruh cache `storefront:products:*` akan di-flush
```php
public function getProducts(Request $request)
{
    $cacheKey = CacheService::key(CacheService::STOREFRONT_PRODUCTS, [
        'category' => $request->category,
        'keyword'  => $request->keyword,
        'sort'     => $request->get('sort', 'newest'),
        'page'     => $request->get('page', 1),
    ]);

    return Cache::remember($cacheKey, CacheService::TTL_STOREFRONT, function () use ($request) {
        // ... query existing yang sama persis ...
    });
}
```

**`getArimaRecommendations()`** — Sudah menggunakan cache, hanya refactor ke `CacheService` constants untuk konsistensi.

