### Fase 3: Caching Layer — Admin Panel Dashboard & Daftar

#### [MODIFY] [AdminDashboardController.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/Diana_fashion/diana_fashion_app/app/Http/Controllers/Admin/AdminDashboardController.php)

**`getMetrics()`** — Cache TTL: 5 menit
- Query agregasi berat (4x SUM/COUNT + 1x GROUP BY) di-cache per hari
- Di-invalidasi otomatis oleh `OrderObserver` saat ada transaksi baru
```php
$cacheKey = CacheService::key(CacheService::DASHBOARD_METRICS, [
    'date' => now()->format('Y-m-d'),
]);
return Cache::remember($cacheKey, CacheService::TTL_DASHBOARD, fn () => /* existing query */);
```

#### [MODIFY] [AdminProductController.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/Diana_fashion/diana_fashion_app/app/Http/Controllers/Admin/AdminProductController.php)

**`index()`** — Cache TTL: 5 menit
- Cache per kombinasi: `keyword`, `low_stock`, `all`, `page`
- Di-invalidasi oleh `ProductObserver`
- Method `store()`, `update()`, `destroy()` → **tidak di-cache** (operasi write)

