**`getHistory()`** — Cache TTL: 5 menit
- Cache per kombinasi: `channel`, `status`, `start_date`, `end_date`, `keyword`, `page`
- Di-invalidasi oleh `OrderObserver`

#### [MODIFY] [AdminCustomerController.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/Diana_fashion/diana_fashion_app/app/Http/Controllers/Admin/AdminCustomerController.php)

**`index()`** — Cache TTL: 5 menit | Di-invalidasi oleh `UserObserver`

#### [MODIFY] [AdminStaffController.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/Diana_fashion/diana_fashion_app/app/Http/Controllers/Admin/AdminStaffController.php)

**`index()`** — Cache TTL: 5 menit | Di-invalidasi oleh `UserObserver`

#### [MODIFY] [ArimaController.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/Diana_fashion/diana_fashion_app/app/Http/Controllers/Admin/ArimaController.php)

**`getConfig()`** — Cache TTL: 1 jam
- Di-invalidasi secara **manual** saat `saveConfig()` dipanggil: `Cache::forget(CacheService::ARIMA_CONFIG)`

**`getLogs()`** — Cache TTL: 2 menit
- Di-invalidasi secara **manual** setelah `runPrediction()` dan `runGlobalPrediction()` selesai

