### Fase 4: Caching Layer — POS Terminal

#### [MODIFY] [PosController.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/Diana_fashion/diana_fashion_app/app/Http/Controllers/PosController.php)

**`searchProducts()`** — Cache TTL: 5 menit
- Cache per kombinasi: `keyword`, `category`
- Di-invalidasi oleh `ProductObserver`

**`getOnlineQueue()`** — Cache TTL: 1 menit
- Antrean bersifat near-real-time, TTL sangat pendek
- Di-invalidasi oleh `OrderObserver` saat ada order web baru atau perubahan status

**`processCheckout()`**, **`validateQueue()`**, **`validateHeldCart()`** — **Tidak di-cache** (operasi write/mutasi)

